If you want this to work in your startup.jl, you can do
```atreplinit() do repl
    try
        @eval using ReplMaker
        @async initrepl(apropos; prompt_text="search&gt; ", prompt_color=:magenta, start_key=')', mode_name="search_mode")

    catch err
        @warn err
    end
end```
This should probably be added to the readme. I'm glad you like the package!

